Our friend Ali decided to take out his Viper ACR & Corvette C8 Targa for a quick shoot. Dodge’s best muscle car and Chevrolet’s newest performance vehicle. 

Special thanks to our team :

Owner @im.ali.khan

Instagram: @carswithoutlimits 
Host - @shaw416 
Manager - @indujan_
FaceBook https://www.facebook.com/CarsWithoutLimits
Twitter https://twitter.com/CarsWithoutLimi 

Production Team:
Paul Saini: @paulsaini_ 
Zach - @zacharyjguy
Max - @maxparkesphoto
Abd - @therealabd

Ali Khan @im.ali.khan
